metadata.name: TokeYo Bears #1
metadata.description: TokeYo Bears is the result of TokyoPunk#420 and Horror Bears falling in love! They have given us 420 TokeYo Bears! All of them are unique with their own distinct personality, but the one thing they have in common is that they are awesome! This is the first collection from the TokeYo 420 brand, co-founded by c0mic and HorrorBears.
